title: The Hooded Horseman {1952-53 & 1954-56 Complete Series}
description: The Hooded Horseman - Yes, pardner...BUD FRASER has developed a handy knack of looking into ruckuses...ever since his sheriff father shot it out with bandits back in Mesa City and died with his guns smoking! From that day, Bud has packed those guns...hunting down outlawry with his dog FLASH...and smashing it in the forbidding black garb of THE HOODED HORSEMAN!
